Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 5.6 19/41] drm/amdgpu: Use GEM obj reference for KFD BOs
Date:   Fri, 22 May 2020 10:49:36 -0400
Message-Id: <20200522144959.434379-19-sashal@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.25.1
